Plot: After the sudden loss of her single mother, Dakota Barabe finds a gerbil inhabiting the late Ms. Barabe's trailer. Could this be her Mama, back from the Void as a furry omen? Will the trailer park hottie Jackson finally notice Dakota?
Title: The Reincarnation Of Ms. Barabe
Actors: Katie Ailion, Jim Babel, Kyle Bell, Kelsey Buterbaugh
